name: Eugene and Katie McKinnon
review: Great place to worship God. A caring pastor, elders, and deacons. A fellowship of loving Christians. The Word of God is preached clearly and the sacraments are rightly administered. Come worship with us.

name: Steven Welch
review: Though I've never been here, I'm sure it's great, since, you know, it's Presbyterian, even though they believe in common grace.

name: David Vreken
review: A welcoming place with reformed Biblical preaching and singing of hymns.
